metadata.name: Vagabond #1
metadata.description: 6666 Vagrants leaving their old world behind to seek new opportunities. The world they had come to dislike. They left one by one. That world had wanted them out; That world had wanted to destroy their lives; That world had wanted them dead. They took part of their home with them, for they knew they could not bring all of it. But enough for a new world. One world. A world of their own.
